Russian /ˈrʌʃən/

1. ADJ Russian means belonging or relating to Russia, or to its people, language, or culture. 俄罗斯的 

例： ...the Russian parliament. ...俄罗斯国会。 

2. N-COUNT A Russian is a Russian citizen, or a person of Russian origin. 俄罗斯人 

例： Three-quarters of Russians live in cities. 四分之三的俄罗斯人住在城市里。 

3. N-UNCOUNT Russian is the language spoken in Russia. 俄语

